-- Brazil's Bradesco taps Le Grazie to head asset management unit
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal
-- Mon Dec 08, 2014 03:05PM EST
-- None



SAO PAULO, Dec 8 (Reuters) - Banco Bradesco SA <BBDC4.SA>, Brazil's No. 2 private-sector bank, on Monday tapped Reinaldo Le Grazie to head its asset management unit.

